    animal`),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},"["),n("i"),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},"]"),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},"."),a("span",{class:"token function"},"mover"),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},"("),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},")"),a("span",{class:"token punctuation"},";"),a("span",{class:"token comment"},"//como será o movimento desse animal?"),n(`
